                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ባቢል</foreign>
               <rs type="root"/>
                    </form>
               <sense xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann" xml:id="Dmain"> “nomen avis fictae: <foreign xml:lang="gez">አዕዋፈ፡ ባቢል፡ ዘውእቱ፡ አጎርጋናት፡ ፫፻</foreign>, Lib. Myst. Crediderim esse aves illas Muhammedieas <foreign xml:lang="ar">ابابيل</foreign> <ref cRef="Sur." loc="105,3">Sur. 105,3</ref>”, Lud. </sense>
               
            <sense xml:lang="en" source="#traces" xml:id="Tmain">
                        <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez">
                            <quote>bābil</quote>
                        </cit> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos>, meaning unknown in the present context, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወይኩን፡ ሩጸትከ፡ ከማሁ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ድምፅ፡ ወስርር፡ እምሥራቅ፡ እስከ፡ ምዕራብ፡ እምሰሜን፡ እስከ፡ ደቡብ፡ እምድር፡ እስከ፡ ባቢል፡ ነፋስ፡</foreign> ‘<cit type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                            <quote>e la tua corsa sia come quello, senza rumore; vola dall’oriente, dal settentrione al meridione, dalla terra fino al vento bābil</quote>
                        </cit>’ <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Marrassini2003GabraManfasQeddusTextus"/>
                            <citedRange unit="page"> 62 (ed.)</citedRange>
                        </bibl>, <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Marrassini2003GabraManfasQeddusVersio"/>
                            <citedRange unit="p"> 22 (tr.)</citedRange>
                        </bibl>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰሪሮ፡ ከመ፡ ንስር። ወዓዲመ፡ በሰረገላ፡ ባቢል፡ ነፋስ፡</foreign> ‘<cit type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                            <quote>volando come un’aquila, e inoltre su un carro di vento bābil</quote>
                        </cit>’ <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Marrassini2003GabraManfasQeddusTextus"/>
                            <citedRange unit="page">114 (ed.)</citedRange>
                        </bibl>, <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Marrassini2003GabraManfasQeddusVersio"/>
                            <citedRange unit="p"> 39 (tr.)</citedRange>
                        </bibl> (‘«Nomen avis fictae» in <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Dillmann1865Lexicon"/>
                            <citedRange unit="page"> 516</citedRange>
                        </bibl>; un serpente (da Daniele) in <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Kur1972MarhaKrestos"/>
                            <citedRange unit="page"> 50 (ed.)</citedRange>
                        </bibl>, <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Kur1972MarhaKrestosV"/>
                            <citedRange unit="page"> 46 (tr.)</citedRange>
                        </bibl>. L’edizione etiopica ha <foreign xml:lang="am">እስከ፡ ሰማይ፡</foreign> <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:GadlaGabraManfasQeddus1961"/>
                            <citedRange unit="page"> 39</citedRange>
                        </bibl>.’ <bibl>
                            <ptr target="bm:Marrassini2003GabraManfasQeddusVersio"/>
                            <citedRange unit="page"> 22 n. 101</citedRange>
                        </bibl>) </sense>
